data.name: label3.Text
data.value: Our Triple Rooms are just what you need! With enough space for three guests, these rooms are perfect for groups who want to stay together while still enjoying plenty of comfort. Relax in cozy beds, take advantage of modern amenities, and make memories in a space designed for sharing. Whether it’s a fun vacation or a quick getaway, our Triple Rooms have everything to make your stay enjoyable.
